[
  {
    "startTime": 3.606,
    "endTime": 8.21,
    "text": "So, Penny tells me you're working as a waitress to put yourself through grad school."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.21,
    "endTime": 9.200000000000001,
    "text": "That's pretty great."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.2,
    "endTime": 10.062999999999999,
    "text": "What are you studying?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.063,
    "endTime": 11.504000000000001,
    "text": "Microbiology."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.504,
    "endTime": 15.134,
    "text": "Oh, cool. So you could study me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.596,
    "endTime": 17.989,
    "text": "I don't understand."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.873,
    "endTime": 22.753,
    "text": "Microbiology is the study of tiny living things."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.753,
    "endTime": 24.899,
    "text": "I know. I'm studying it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.227,
    "endTime": 33.026,
    "text": "And I said you could study me 'cause I'm a tiny living thing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.098,
    "endTime": 35.4,
    "text": "It's a joke."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.4,
    "endTime": 36.504,
    "text": "Are you sure?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.33,
    "endTime": 43.614999999999995,
    "text": "Do you like science fiction?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.615,
    "endTime": 44.578,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.578,
    "endTime": 45.909000000000006,
    "text": "Role-playing games?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.909,
    "endTime": 48.668,
    "text": "Like in the bedroom or like Dungeons and Dragons?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.668,
    "endTime": 50.138,
    "text": "Either."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.138,
    "endTime": 51.031,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.682,
    "endTime": 56.34,
    "text": "-Do you like ... -It's gonna be a long night."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.34,
    "endTime": 57.466,
    "text": "Yeah, well, it's your fault."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.466,
    "endTime": 60.168,
    "text": "I had to ask; you didn't have to say yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.67,
    "endTime": 63.702,
    "text": "You like magic?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.702,
    "endTime": 65.576,
    "text": "-Not really. -Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.365,
    "endTime": 70.405,
    "text": "Long, long night."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.16,
    "endTime": 75.847,
    "text": "How about computers? Do you like computers?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.847,
    "endTime": 76.815,
    "text": "I use them."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.815,
    "endTime": 78.365,
    "text": "I don't like them."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.91,
    "endTime": 83.865,
    "text": "Okay. Puppies, where do you stand on puppies?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.872,
    "endTime": 86.685,
    "text": "A puppy once bit my face."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.67,
    "endTime": 89.503,
    "text": "Of course it did."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.503,
    "endTime": 92.132,
    "text": "How about that? Einstein was wrong."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.132,
    "endTime": 92.554,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.554,
    "endTime": 96.242,
    "text": "Approaching the speed of light doesn't slow down time; approaching them does."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.0,
    "endTime": 101.043,
    "text": "Excuse me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.043,
    "endTime": 103.58000000000001,
    "text": "Ugh, damn, it's my mother."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.58,
    "endTime": 104.62,
    "text": "Are you going to answer it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.62,
    "endTime": 105.88300000000001,
    "text": "Uh, I'm torn."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.883,
    "endTime": 107.03399999999999,
    "text": "She might be dying."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.034,
    "endTime": 108.756,
    "text": "You know, wouldn't wanna miss that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.0,
    "endTime": 114.742,
    "text": "On the other hand, if I let it go to voicemail, I could play it over and over."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.299,
    "endTime": 118.98700000000001,
    "text": "I know how you feel."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.987,
    "endTime": 121.032,
    "text": "My mother makes me crazy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.032,
    "endTime": 123.77,
    "text": "Not as crazy as my mother makes me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.77,
    "endTime": 124.609,
    "text": "Oh yeah?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.609,
    "endTime": 128.225,
    "text": "Does your mother call you every day at work to see if you've had a healthy lunch?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.225,
    "endTime": 132.482,
    "text": "My mother calls me at work to see if I had a healthy bowel movement."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.622,
    "endTime": 141.88500000000002,
    "text": "Okay, well, does she lay out your clothes for you in the morning like you're nine years old?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.885,
    "endTime": 143.69799999999998,
    "text": "You live with your mother?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.698,
    "endTime": 145.48000000000002,
    "text": "No, that's the sad part."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.453,
    "endTime": 149.345,
    "text": "Oh, okay. Check this out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.345,
    "endTime": 154.391,
    "text": "My mother made me wear rubber gloves to kindergarten so I wouldn't pick up a disease from the other children."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.87,
    "endTime": 156.761,
    "text": "That's nothing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.761,
    "endTime": 161.15099999999998,
    "text": "I couldn't ride a bicycle 'cause my mother was afraid I'd hit a bump and lose my virginity."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.151,
    "endTime": 164.83800000000002,
    "text": "Oh, wow. You didn't, did you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.838,
    "endTime": 166.08599999999998,
    "text": "Not on a bicycle."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.086,
    "endTime": 167.72,
    "text": "In a Camry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.271,
    "endTime": 172.75799999999998,
    "text": "Corolla."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.65,
    "endTime": 175.81,
    "text": "-More wine? - I'd love some."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.81,
    "endTime": 179.716,
    "text": "Listen, you have to come to Shabbat dinner at my house sometime."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.716,
    "endTime": 180.37900000000002,
    "text": "Why?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.379,
    "endTime": 186.927,
    "text": "A Catholic girl like you wearing a big cross like that might just give my mother the big brain aneurism I've been hoping for."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.78,
    "endTime": 194.363,
    "text": "Okay, but only if you come to Sunday dinner at my house wearing a yarmulke."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.32,
    "endTime": 196.23999999999998,
